                     </persName>
                     
                  , a dollar value five shillings, and two shillings in silver, a two-pound bank-note, and a one-pound bank-note, the property of 
                     <persName id="t18051204-48-person569">
                        Joseph 
                        Cantley
                     <interp inst="t18051204-48-person569" type="surname" value="Cantley"></interp>
